long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adservice is a library to used manage ads. With this extension, publishers using this library can see some informations about their site. For example, https://www.milliyet.com.tr is our publisher. If this site is open, this extension works. If site isn't our publisher, this extension won't work and will see "Adservice isn't active."
